# copy or symlink your /etc/hosts content here
#
# to create custom blocker just add new files
# under this folder, for example:
#
# ---------------------------
# hosts/work
# ---------------------------
# 127.0.0.1 www.some.com
# 127.0.0.1 www.other.com
# 127.0.0.1 www.domain.com
# ---------------------------
#
# this will block all three domains contained in
# the hosts/work file
